Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.01,0:00:12.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西历2313年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是一个因新生地球政府的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:19.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而平稳迈向统一的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时的Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:29.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}剧场预告篇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐呐  玛丽  之前的那个寺院很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好闲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.44,0:00:36.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.69,0:00:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说地球非常和平吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提我是立体影像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人待在吠陀那里也没事干
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:46.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人问你这个啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.17,0:00:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这么闲怎么撑到剧场版出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.49,0:00:51.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  大家好大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:56.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我已经升仙了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.64,0:00:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个桥段已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.53,0:01:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天怎么跑出来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  天国开了家很有趣的店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你们很闲  我就来请你们去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不想去哥哥你那边啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.45,0:01:12.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.37,0:01:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会送你们回来的  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:17.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（唔  这样的话…）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  就当是杀杀时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:28.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,800)}（※忘记把莱尔放进来了）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.16,0:01:45.23,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Good面包店）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good面包店…？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.31,0:01:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你想带我们来的就是这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.98,0:01:54.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说啦  这里的东西很好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  我带客人来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.67,0:02:05.89,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（欢迎光临）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.41,0:02:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些人应该是第一次见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么总觉得好像认识他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们店的面包都是刚烤好的  都很好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:15.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（很好吃哦）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实挺好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我请客  放开了吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的熊猫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俄罗斯的暴熊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.07,0:02:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.08,0:02:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.40,0:02:42.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  佩丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安  安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:02:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  安德烈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.41,0:03:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊  玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:34.19,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为豆沙面包就应该是烂馅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈里路亚却觉得粒馅比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.82,0:03:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩得还挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还见到了那些怀念的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.58,0:04:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧场再续…？



